# PWA page layout patterns (HIVE073)

## Single title

- One source of truth for the page title
- If `listTitle` === `title`, use `hideListHeaderWhenRedundant` on PurityListPage
- Avoid redundant listTitle/listDescription with the page header

## Single Create button

- One place for “Create / New”: page header (`actions` on PurityPageWrapper)
- Do not duplicate the button in the card and in the header

## Datagrid for lists

- Use Datagrid + ListWithController for tabular lists (filters, sort, pagination)
- Reference: PaymentsList, SecretsList, WorkspacesList

## Breadcrumbs

- Use PurityPageWrapper or PurityPageHeader for consistent breadcrumbs
- Do not use Chakra `Breadcrumb.Root` directly
